feed.title: Stefan’s Blog
feed.subtitle: New year's resolution to start writing more often. Blog about programming, travel, life, and learning. Thoughts are my own.

entry.title: Into the New Year!
entry.content:
Decided to set up this blog for the new year. Not sure what to fill it up with yet but looking into Jekyll is nice. Hopefully I can pick this up rather quickly and it’ll be easier to make blog posts down the line.

I’m currently celebrating the holidays in New York City, flew down to see my family and now I’m getting ready to go back to Seattle.

-Stefan
